Subject: [PATCH 29/33] netlink: add netlink handler for reset (--reset)

Implement "ethtool --reset <dev>" using netlink interface command
ETHNL_CMD_ACT_RESET.

Signed-off-by: Michal Kubecek <mkubecek@suse.cz>
